CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 1, 1957, pg. 22, reads: "Mrs. Dandridge Honored - Business and Professional Women who celebrated their Founder's Day Sunday, at Warren Methodist Church, honored Mrs. Nathaniel Dandridge, center, by giving her the Sojourner Truth Award for her community activities. Pictured, left to right: Mrs. Marian Bryant, president of the Pittsburgh chapter; Mrs. Lenore Rainey, Mrs. Dandridge, Mrs. Florence Allen Holmes of New York, guest speaker, and Mrs. Julia Leach, chairman of the committee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Business and Professional Women, Pittsburgh Chapter president Marian Bryant, Lenore Rainey, honoree Helen Dandridge, guest speaker Florence Allen Holmes, and Julia Leach gathered in Warren Methodist Church for BPA Founder's Day celebration
